paper_metadata.extraction_summary: The paper discusses the accessibility of occupational therapy services for patients with hereditary transthyretin amyloidosis (ATTRv) in Spain. It mentions the TTR gene and the Val50Met variant but does not provide detailed genetic variant information or penetrance data.
